content:
As a team lead, it’s important to stay on top of everyone’s schedules. Approve time sheets and time-off requests by agent or by object type.

Workforce Engagement is available in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Shift Scheduling is available in the Contact Center Stock Keeping Unit (SKU), Einstein 1 Service Edition, and Service Suites.

To approve time sheets and absences: 

Shift Scheduling Planner

OR

Workforce Engagement Planner

Open Service Resources from the App Launcher. Click the name of a service resource. Click Related. Click a time sheet from the Time Sheets list or an absence from the Absences list. Click to edit the Status field. Change the status to Submitted. Save your changes.

Preparing for Time Sheets and Resource Absences
title: Approving Time Sheets and Time-Off Requests in Service Cloud
